            <title>[CASSANDRA-5786] Thrift cas() method crashes if input columns are not sorted.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5786</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CassandraServer#cas() use UnsortedColumns for the &quot;updates&quot;, which might result later to a&lt;/p&gt;
