                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13714967" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 22 Jul 2013 07:10:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching simple patch to switch to TreeMap. I&apos;m also including a minor optimization that switch to ArraySorted when we clone the updates in Commit#updatesWithPaxosTime.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13714997" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 22 Jul 2013 08:02:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Disregard the comment above. For normal updates we keep columns unsorted until they are applied to the memtable and we should probably do that here too for consistency. So attaching patch that makes sure we don&apos;t assume the columns are sorted when deserializing for paxos.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
